<div class="how-long-will-you-keep-my-personal-information">
<h2 class="privacy__question" id="how-long-will-you-keep-my-personal-information">إلى متى ستحتفظون بمعلوماتي الشخصيّة؟</h2> 

<div class="privacy__answer hidden-closed" >
